    "postDataSections": [
      {
        "title": "数据处理",
        "segments": [
          "实验内容：三线摆和扭摆实验\n三、数据记录 上传原始数据（教师签字盖章版本）",
          "表1，有关长度测量的实验数据表 （注意规范读数）",
          "表2，累积法测摆动30个周期所需的时间 三线摆：",
          "扭摆：",
          "四、计算处理\n三线摆实验\n1. 求悬盘绕中心轴的转动惯量",
          {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "/assets/configs_images/exp_three_line_torsion_pendulum_img_018.png",
            "inline": true,
            "width": "16.9639047348994px",
            "height": "16.1928181560403px"
          },
          "（",
          {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "/assets/configs_images/exp_three_line_torsion_pendulum_img_019.png",
            "inline": true,
            "width": "49.34954104698px",
            "height": "19.2771644714766px"
          },
          "）=",
          {
            "nodeId": "S4",
            "width": "80px"
          },
          "\n2. 悬盘加圆环绕中心轴的转动惯量",
          {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "/assets/configs_images/exp_three_line_torsion_pendulum_img_020.png",
            "inline": true,
            "width": "14.6506449983222px",
            "height": "15.8072748666108px"
          },
          "（",
          {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "/assets/configs_images/exp_three_line_torsion_pendulum_img_021.png",
            "inline": true,
            "width": "49.34954104698px",
